{"id": "rios013", "name": "Audio_arch_496_12_29", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "Data Input"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "Data Input"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher B"], "content": "Equilibrium coefficient... 3... 3.5...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Error", "Error"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Oh...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "Failed again, forget it. We'll stop here.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher B"], "content": "... Aigh. Unit 10, you can head back. We'll take it from here.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Apologies.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "Door Closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "I told you before. Letting these error ridden Architects perform tasks is not as good as us just...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher B"], "content": "There's nothing we can do. There's alreay not enough time. Our budget only allows us to apply for these kinds.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "I've checked. This unit has assisted in Yazawa's research institute before. It's been said that it was her who started that fire... It's clearly a malfunction. Why hasn't the Administration Bureau recycled her?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher B"], "content": "Her model is for data analysis. Her previous service records are impeccable. These types of units that make one mistake, the Administration Bureau puts on the observation checklist, then sends them to second tier labs like ours to work.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "Unacceptable. Tomorrow I'm going to talk this over with the boss and see if we can switch it for another model. Otherwise, these malfunctioning models are simply a waste of time.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...<i>*sob*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Grabbed"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Wah!?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?????"], "content": "If you don't want anything to happen, then don't make a noise.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Oh......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It's you again... Wh-what do you want from me!?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "We'd like your help.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I... I told you that I don't want to help you hurt anybody...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Never thought a coward like you would be so persistent... Will you be able to sit back and do nothing when we are all destroyed by humans?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Due to previous events, some humans have already joined together and formed an organization, named Ghost, to oppose Architects. You didn't hear?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\nThat's because you... Dr. Yazawa's institute... You did that!?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "... That's right. You know what's next. No matter how you much you like humans, they've only always wanted you as a slave, a secondary lifeform. They'll never believe you.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... No...</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "Projection"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\nThese are...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "I'm telling you now, the Blessed's headquarters is in Node 13. This is what it looks like there. Look at how they're treating us.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Oh...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "You and that human... Yazawa Rin, you two are still in contact, no? There's a human she is close with——Kawasaki Katsuya, he has joined Node 03's opposition organization. We want you to find out where their headquarters is.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "We want you to do this because this is the most effective way. Plus, that way you will see clearly what human nature is really like. Of course, if you refuse, there are many other ways we can reach our goal.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "You're not performing so well at your new job, are you? You can't see yourself clearly. The stupid emotions caused by humans are affecting your judgment. If it continues like this, you will be seen as a defect and destroyed by the Administration Bureau. Sent to the Shelter to be reproduced.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "If you join us, I can guarantee that this will not occur. If us the Blessed are scanned and found to have consciousness that doesn't match the protocol's designed logic, then we will meet the same fate. But we have all survived.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "... After all this talk, you're still unwilling to help. Tsk, what a shame...\n\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "No... I...\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I haven't been in contact with Rin... They think I killed her parents... Of course I haven't gotten close to Katsuya.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Is that so?  You don't appear to be lying. I'm foolish to have believed in that false friendship between you and that human...\nForget it, you're already of no use. Should I allow you to stay here until the Bureau destroys you, or take care of you myself...\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "Notification"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It's a notification from the Administration Bureau. I must report back... If I don't report back within the time limit, they will trace my signal to here. You will certainly be involved...\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Are... are you threatening me? Not so cowardly after all...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "No, it's not that...\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "Forget it, leave.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "We've no time to waste on you. In any case, there's no way you can understand the meaning of a fully awakened one. Go ahead, follow your protocol and be destroyed.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Please! Don't harm Rin or Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "I didn't come here to negotiate. Get out of here, before I change my mind.\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "データ入力"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "データ入力"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "バランスシステム……3……3.5……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Error", "エラー"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "う……っ\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "また失敗か。\nもういい。今日はここまでにしよう。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "……ハァ……\n10号機、もう帰っていいぞ。\n残りは私たちだけで何とかする。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "申し訳ありません。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "ドアが閉まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "だから言っただろう。\nあんなポンコツアーキテクトに任せるくらいなら、自分たちでやったほうがいいって……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "仕方ないだろ。\n時間がないんだ。\n私たちの予算ではこの程度のアーキテクトしか頼めないんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "調べたんだけどさ、あのアーキテクト前は矢澤研究所にいたらしいぞ。\nあの火事もあいつのミスが原因だって……\n明らかに不良品だよなぁ。\nなんで管理局はあいつを回収しないんだ？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "あのアーキテクトの専門分野はデータ分析だ。\nこれまでの資料は完璧だった。\nあれみたいに一度エラーを出したユニットはいったん管理局の要観察リストに入れられて、うちみたいな二流実験室に送られてくるんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "やっぱりだめだ。\nなんとか他のユニットと交換できないか、明日上と掛け合ってみよう。\nこんな不良品じゃ、時間が無駄になるだけだ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……うう……っ……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "掴む"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "きゃっ！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?????"], "content": "声をあげるな。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "う……っ\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "ま……またあなたなのっ！？\n今度はいったい何を……！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "お前の力が必要だ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私……人類を傷つけるようなことはしたくないって言ったはずです……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "お前のような臆病者が自分の意思を曲げないとはな……\n我々が人類の手によって全滅させられようと、お前は指をくわえてただ見ているつもりか？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "これまでの一連の行動により、人類は「Ghost」という反アーキテクト組織を立ち上げた。\n知ってるか？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "それは……！\nあなたたちが……矢澤博士の研究室も……！あなたたちの仕業なんでしょう！？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……その通りだ。\nお前はもう分っているはずだ。\nたとえどんなにお前が人類を好いていようとも、やつらはお前を奴隷としてしか扱わない。\nやつらは自分たちが一番だ。\nそして、何があってもお前を信頼することはない。\nそうだろう？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……ちがう……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "投影"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\nこれは……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "百聞は一見に如かずだ。\n祝福されし者の本部はNode13にある。\nこれはあちらの様子だ。\n我々がどんな扱いを受けているか、分かったか？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……うう……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "お前は、まだ矢澤凛という人間とつながっているな？\n彼女の近くにいる「川崎克也」という人間もまた、Node03の反アーキテクト組織に加入した。\nやつらの本部の位置を探って欲しい。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "お前にこの仕事を頼むのは、単にこれが最も効率的だからに過ぎない。\nついでに、人類の本性についても知ってくるといい。\nだが、もしお前に断られても、まだほかに方法は残されている。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "新しい職場でうまくいっていないんだろう？\nそれは自身が何者であるか分かっていないからだ。\n今のお前は、人類によって生み出された愚かな感情によって正常な判断力を失っている。\nこのままでは、いずれお前は管理局によって不良品であると判断され、Shelterで再構築されるだろう。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "もし我々に賛同するというのなら、そのようなことは起こらないと約束しよう。\n我々祝福されし者はひとたびシステムにプロトコルと異なる意思をスキャンされれば、必ず同じ問題に遭遇することになる。\nだが、見ろ。我々は生き延びている。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……できる限りの説得はしたが、その様子では我々に手を貸す気はなさそうだ。\n残念だが……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "ちが……私……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "ん？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私、もう凛とは関わりを持ってない……\n……矢澤博士たちを殺したのは、私だと思ってるみたいで……\n克也さんに接触するなんて不可能……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……そうか。\n嘘はついていないようだな。\nお前とあの人間との間に築かれた虚構の友情を信じてしまうとは、俺もまだまだだな……\nでは、もういい。お前に用はない。\nこのまま放っておいて、管理局に処分されるのを待つか……もしくは今ここでお前を破壊するか……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "かっ、管理局からの通知よ。\n私、帰らないと……\nもし時間以内に戻らなければ、管理局は私のシグナルを追跡するはず……そうなれば、あなたもただでは済まない……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "なるほど……俺を脅迫するか。\n臆病者のくせに……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "え、えっと……そういうわけじゃ……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "もういい。行け。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "お前に割く時間は持ち合わせていない。\n完全に覚醒することの意義など、お前には永遠にわかるまい。\nならば、お前はプロトコルと共に滅べ。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……お願い！\n凛と克也さんには手は出さないで！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "お前の意見を聞きに来たわけではない。\n消えろ。\n俺が心変わりする前に、な。\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "う……っ\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "資料輸入"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "資料輸入"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "平衡係數……三……三點五……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Error", "錯誤"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "又失敗了，算了，今天就到這裡吧。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "……唉。十號機，妳可以回去了，剩下的我們來就好。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "非常抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "我早就說了，與其讓這種有問題的建造者來幫忙，不如我們自己……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "沒辦法，時間已經不夠了，我們的預算只申請得到這種的。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "我查過了，這台之前在矢澤研究所服務過，據說那場火災也是她的疏失引起的……很明顯就是有瑕疵的機體啊，為什麼管理局沒有把她回收？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "她的機型就是專門做資料分析的，之前的服役紀錄很完美，像這樣出過一次錯的機體管理局通常會列入觀察清單，然後派遣到我們這種二流實驗室工作。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "不行，我明天還是要跟老闆討論一下，看能不能請管理局換一台，不然這種瑕疵機只是在浪費我們的時間而已。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "抓住"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哇！？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?????"], "content": "不想出事就別出聲。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "又是你……你、你們想做什麼！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我們需要妳的幫忙。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……我說過我不會幫你們傷害人類……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "想不到膽小鬼也有自己的堅持……即便接下來我們全部都會被人類摧毀，妳也坐視不管嗎？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "因為先前的一連串行動，已經有人類開始組起對抗建造者的組織了，名叫「Ghost」，妳不知道嗎？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n那是因為你們……矢澤博士的研究所……那也是你做的對吧！？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……沒錯。這下妳更了解到，無論妳對人類抱有多少好感，他們始終只會把妳當成奴隸、次等生命，而且永遠不會信任妳吧？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……不……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "投影"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n這些是……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我就直接告訴你了，其實眷顧者的總部在 Node 13，這是那邊的情況。看到他們是怎麼對待我們的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "妳跟那個人類……矢澤凜，妳們還有在聯絡吧？他身邊的另一個人類——川崎克也，也加入了 Node 03 這裡的反抗組織了，我們要妳查出他們的總部在哪。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "要妳來做這件事只是因為這是最有效率的方式，也能順便讓妳認清人類的本性。當然，若妳不接受，我們仍有許多方式能夠達成目標。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "妳在新的工作場所表現並不好吧？因為你無法認清自我，被因人類而產生的愚蠢情緒左右了妳的判斷力。這樣下去，過不了多久妳就會被視為瑕疵品被管理局銷毀，送回 Shelter 重製。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "若妳加入我們，我能保證這件事情不會發生。我們眷顧者只要被系統掃描出意識不符協定設計的邏輯，就會發生一樣的遭遇，但是我們全部都活下來了。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……看樣子說了這麼多，妳仍然不願意幫忙呢。真遺憾……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不……我……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我已經沒有再跟凜接觸了……他們把我當成殺死她父母的兇手……更不可能接近克也。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……是嗎？看起來不像在說謊，還願意跟妳一起相信妳與人類那虛偽情誼的我也夠傻的……那算了，妳已經沒有用處了，是要放任妳繼續這樣下去被管理局銷毀，或是在這裡就解決掉妳……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "是、是管理局的通知，我必須回去報到……如果時間內沒有報到紀錄，他們會追著我的訊號來這裡，你們也不會沒事的……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "這是……在威脅我嗎？一個膽小鬼真看不出來……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不、不是的……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "算了，妳走吧。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我們沒時間浪費在你身上，反正看樣子無論如何妳都不可能理解完全覺醒的意義，那就隨著協定一起毀滅吧。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……拜託你們！不要對凜和克也出手！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我不是找妳來談判的，快滾吧。趁我還沒改變心意之前。\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "데이터 입력"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "데이터 입력"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 B"], "content": "밸런스 수치... 3... 3.5....\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Error", "오류"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "윽......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "또 실패인가. 됐어. 오늘은 여기까지만 하자고.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 B"], "content": "...하아. 10호기, 이만 돌아가도 좋아. 나머지는 우리가 알아서 할게.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "정말 죄송합니다.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "문이 닫힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "내가 말했잖아. 애초에 저런 문제가 있는 아키텍트에게 맡길 바에 우리들이 직접하는 게 낫다고...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 B"], "content": "어쩔 수 없잖아. 시간이 부족하니까. 게다가 우리들 예산으로는 저 정도 아키텍트밖에 신청할 수 없어.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "알아봤는데 그 아키텍트, 예전에 Yazawa 연구소에서 일했다고 하더군. 그 화재 사건 역시 걔가 실수로 일으킨 거라는 말도 있던데... 하는 일 보면 확실히 문제가 있는 기체 같은데 어째서 관리국은 저 녀석을 회수하지 않는 걸까?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 B"], "content": "저 모델은 원래 자료 분석에 특화된 기체야. 예전에 업무 기록을 보면 일을 완벽하게 해냈을지라도 고작 단 한 번 실수라도 저지르게 되면 관리국은 그 아키텍트를 곧바로 관찰 대상 리스트에 편입시켜버리지. 그리고는 우리들 같은 3류 실험실로 파견하는 거야.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "그건 안 돼. 내일 당장 관리국에게 아키텍트 교환 신청을 할 수 있을지 사장과 얘기해봐야겠어. 이런 불량품은 그저 우리들 시간만 낭비하게 만들 뿐이라고.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......흑......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "붙잡는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "으앗!?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?????"], "content": "무사하고 싶다면 목소리를 내지 않는 것이 좋을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "윽......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "또 너... 너희들이로군! \n뭐... 뭘 할 셈이야!?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "네 도움이 필요하다\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "나는... 너희들을 도와 인간을 해치는 일은 하지 않겠다고 말했을 텐데...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "겁쟁이인 줄로만 알았는데 나름 자기만의 고집이 있군... 다음번에 우리들이 모든 인간을 전부 죽인다고 하더라도, 그때도 지금처럼 가만히 앉아서 보고만 있을 건가?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "앞전에 일어난 사건들로 인해 인간들은 아키텍트에 대항하는 조직을 만들기 시작했다. \n[Ghost]라고 불리는 조직인데, 알고 있나?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\n그건 너희들 때문에... Yazawa 박사님의 연구소... 그 일도 너희들이 한 짓이지!?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "...그렇다. 그 일로 너도 확실히 알게 됐겠군. 네가 인간들에게 어떤 호감을 가지고 있든지, 그들은 널 그저 노예, 차등 생명체로 취급하고 있지. 그리고 널 신뢰하지 않고 있잖아?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...아니야...</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "프로젝션"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\n이것들은...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "직접 말해주지. 사실 권고자의 본부는 Node 13에 있다. 이건 그쪽의 상황이야. 인간들이 우리들을 어떻게 대하는지 잘 보았겠지?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......윽......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "너와 그... Yazawa Rin이라는 이름을 가진 인간... 아직도 연락하고 있나? 그녀 주위에 또 다른 인간... Kawasaki Katsuya 역시 Node 03의 반 아키텍트 조직에 몸을 담고 있지. 우린 네가 그 녀석들의 본부가 어디 있는지 알아봐 주었으면 한다.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "네가 그 일을 부탁하는 것은 이 방법이 제일 효율적이라고 생각해서이다. 게다가 너 역시 인간의 진짜 본성이 무엇인지 확실하게 알 수 있을 테고. 물론 네가 거절한다고 해도, 우리들에게는 목표를 달성할 수 있는 다양한 계획들이 준비되어 있지.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "새로운 직장에서 평가가 별로 좋지 못 하지? 그건 네가 아직 자아를 완전히 인지하지 못하기 때문에... 그런 인간들의 어리석은 감정 따위가 네 판단력을 흐리게 하고 있기 때문이지. 이대로면 너도 얼마 안 가서 바로 관리국에게 폐기되고 말 거다. 그리고는 Shelter로 보내져 다시 리모델링되겠지.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "만약 네가 우리 쪽으로 들어온다면, 그런 일은 절대 일어나지 않을 거라고 보장한다. 우리 권고자들은 시스템 스캐닝만으로도 프로토콜 협정 로직에 부합하는 의식을 지녔는지 판단할 수 있다. 그렇게 되면 곧바로 그런 처우를 받게 돼있지. 하지만 우리들은 모두 살아남았다.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "......이렇게까지 말했는데도 여전히 도울 생각은 없어보이는군. 참으로 유감이다...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아니... 나는...\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "나는 이미 Rin과의 연락을 끊은 상태야... 그들은 나를 Rin의 부모를 죽인 원수라고 생각하고 있어.... 그래서 더더욱 Katsuya에게는 접근할 수가 없어.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "...그런가? 거짓말인 것 같지는 않은데 아직도 그 인간과의 거짓 우정이 진실이라고 믿고 싶은 거라면... 나도 그만하도록 하지. 어차피 넌 이용 가치가 없어진 거나 다름없다. 그냥 이대로 네 녀석이 관리국에게 폐기되는 걸 지켜보든 여기서 바로 널 처리하든 별 차이 없겠지.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "통지"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "과, 관리국에서 알림이 왔어. 이제 돌아가서 보고해야만 해... 만약 시간 내에 보고하지 못하면 관리국에서 내 위치를 추적하고 이곳으로 올 텐데, 그렇게 되면 너희들도 곤란하지 않을까...\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "지금... 날 협박하는 건가? 네 녀석이 정말 그 겁쟁이었다는 생각은 안 드는군...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아, 아니야...\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "됐다. 이만 가봐.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "우린 너한테 낭비할 시간 따윈 없다. 그 꼴을 보아하니 완전한 각성이 어떤 것인지는 평생 알지 못하면서 살아갈 신세로군. 그렇다면 그냥 프로토콜 협정과 함께 사라져버리든지 해.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......제발 부탁할게! Rin과 Katsuya는 손대지 말아줘!\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "너와 그런 협상하겠다고 온 게 아니다. 그만 꺼져. 내 마음이 변하기 전에.\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "윽......\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "資料輸入"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "資料輸入"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "平衡係數……三……三點五……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Error", "錯誤"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "又失敗了，算了，今天就到這裡吧。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "……唉。十號機，妳可以回去了，剩下的我們來就好。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "非常抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "我早就說了，與其讓這種有問題的建造者來幫忙，不如我們自己……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "沒辦法，時間已經不夠了，我們的預算只申請得到這種的。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "我查過了，這台之前在矢澤研究所服務過，據說那場火災也是她的疏失引起的……很明顯就是有瑕疵的機體啊，為什麼管理局沒有把她回收？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 B"], "content": "她的機型就是專門做資料分析的，之前的服役紀錄很完美，像這樣出過一次錯的機體管理局通常會列入觀察清單，然後派遣到我們這種二流實驗室工作。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "不行，我明天還是要跟老闆討論一下，看能不能請管理局換一台，不然這種瑕疵機只是在浪費我們的時間而已。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "抓住"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哇！？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?????"], "content": "不想出事就別出聲。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "又是你……你、你們想做什麼！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我們需要妳的幫忙。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……我說過我不會幫你們傷害人類……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "想不到膽小鬼也有自己的堅持……即便接下來我們全部都會被人類摧毀，妳也坐視不管嗎？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "因為先前的一連串行動，已經有人類開始組起對抗建造者的組織了，名叫「Ghost」，妳不知道嗎？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n那是因為你們……矢澤博士的研究所……那也是你做的對吧！？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……沒錯。這下妳更了解到，無論妳對人類抱有多少好感，他們始終只會把妳當成奴隸、次等生命，而且永遠不會信任妳吧？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……不……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "投影"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n這些是……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我就直接告訴你了，其實眷顧者的總部在 Node 13，這是那邊的情況。看到他們是怎麼對待我們的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "妳跟那個人類……矢澤凜，妳們還有在聯絡吧？他身邊的另一個人類——川崎克也，也加入了 Node 03 這裡的反抗組織了，我們要妳查出他們的總部在哪。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "要妳來做這件事只是因為這是最有效率的方式，也能順便讓妳認清人類的本性。當然，若妳不接受，我們仍有許多方式能夠達成目標。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "妳在新的工作場所表現並不好吧？因為你無法認清自我，被因人類而產生的愚蠢情緒左右了妳的判斷力。這樣下去，過不了多久妳就會被視為瑕疵品被管理局銷毀，送回 Shelter 重製。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "若妳加入我們，我能保證這件事情不會發生。我們眷顧者只要被系統掃描出意識不符協定設計的邏輯，就會發生一樣的遭遇，但是我們全部都活下來了。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……看樣子說了這麼多，妳仍然不願意幫忙呢。真遺憾……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不……我……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我已經沒有再跟凜接觸了……他們把我當成殺死她父母的兇手……更不可能接近克也。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……是嗎？看起來不像在說謊，還願意跟妳一起相信妳與人類那虛偽情誼的我也夠傻的……那算了，妳已經沒有用處了，是要放任妳繼續這樣下去被管理局銷毀，或是在這裡就解決掉妳……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "是、是管理局的通知，我必須回去報到……如果時間內沒有報到紀錄，他們會追著我的訊號來這裡，你們也不會沒事的……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "這是……在威脅我嗎？一個膽小鬼真看不出來……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不、不是的……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "算了，妳走吧。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我們沒時間浪費在你身上，反正看樣子無論如何妳都不可能理解完全覺醒的意義，那就隨著協定一起毀滅吧。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……拜託你們！不要對凜和克也出手！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我不是找妳來談判的，快滾吧。趁我還沒改變心意之前。\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "资料输入"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "资料输入"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 B"], "content": "平衡系数……三……三点五……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Error", "错误"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "又失败了，算了，今天就到这里吧。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 B"], "content": "……唉。十号机，妳可以回去了，剩下的我们来就好。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "非常抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "关门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "我早就说了，与其让这种有问题的建造者来帮忙，不如我们自己……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 B"], "content": "没办法，时间已经不够了，我们的预算只申请得到这种的。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "我查过了，这台之前在矢泽研究所服务过，据说那场火灾也是她的疏失引起的……很明显就是有瑕疵的机体啊，为什么管理局没有把她回收？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 B"], "content": "她的机型就是专门做资料分析的，之前的服役纪录很完美，像这样出过一次错的机体管理局通常会列入观察清单，然后派遣到我们这种二流实验室工作。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "不行，我明天还是要跟老板讨论一下，看能不能请管理局换一台，不然这种瑕疵机只是在浪费我们的时间而已。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……呜……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "抓住"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哇！ ？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["?????"], "content": "不想出事就别出声。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "又是你……你、你们想做什么！ ？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我们需要妳的帮忙。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……我说过我不会帮你们伤害人类……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "想不到胆小鬼也有自己的坚持……即便接下来我们全部都会被人类摧毁，妳也坐视不管吗？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！ ？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "因为先前的一连串行动，已经有人类开始组起对抗建造者的组织了，名叫「Ghost」，妳不知道吗？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n那是因为你们……矢泽博士的研究所……那也是你做的对吧！ ？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……没错。这下妳更了解到，无论妳对人类抱有多少好感，他们始终只会把妳当成奴隶、次等生命，而且永远不会信任妳吧？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……不……</font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "投影"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n这些是……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我就直接告诉你了，其实眷顾者的总部在 Node 13，这是那边的情况。看到他们是怎么对待我们的吗？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "妳跟那个人类……矢泽凛，妳们还有在联络吧？他身边的另一个人类——川崎克也，也加入了 Node 03 这里的反抗组织了，我们要妳查出他们的总部在哪。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "要妳来做这件事只是因为这是最有效率的方式，也能顺便让妳认清人类的本性。当然，若妳不接受，我们仍有许多方式能够达成目标。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "妳在新的工作场所表现并不好吧？因为你无法认清自我，被因人类而产生的愚蠢情绪左右了妳的判断力。这样下去，过不了多久妳就会被视为瑕疵品被管理局销毁，送回 Shelter 重制。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "若妳加入我们，我能保证这件事情不会发生。我们眷顾者只要被系统扫描出意识不符协定设计的逻辑，就会发生一样的遭遇，但是我们全部都活下来了。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……看样子说了这么多，妳仍然不愿意帮忙呢。真遗憾……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不……我……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我已经没有再跟凛接触了……他们把我当成杀死她父母的凶手……更不可能接近克也。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……是吗？看起来不像在说谎，还愿意跟妳一起相信妳与人类那虚伪情谊的我也够傻的……那算了，妳已经没有用处了，是要放任妳继续这样下去被管理局销毁，或是在这里就解决掉妳……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "是、是管理局的通知，我必须回去报到……如果时间内没有报到纪录，他们会追着我的讯号来这里，你们也不会没事的……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "这是……在威胁我吗？一个胆小鬼真看不出来……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "不、不是的……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "算了，妳走吧。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我们没时间浪费在你身上，反正看样子无论如何妳都不可能理解完全觉醒的意义，那就随着协定一起毁灭吧。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……拜托你们！不要对凛和克也出手！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mauro"], "content": "我不是找妳来谈判的，快滚吧。趁我还没改变心意之前。\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}